3135.title: NAMCO sounds.sea
3135.author: Anonymous
3135.description:
This file replaces many of Swoops sounds with the original sounds from NAMCO's Galaga arcade game. 

If you have problems on the bonus round, try increasing the memory allocation to Swoop, and you should be all set.

3139.title: swoopswmusic.sit

3139.description: Add the TIE-Fighter theme from Star Wars Episode 4 (from the scene after the Millenium Falcon escapes from the Death Star) to Swoop!  A couple of patches are included to do the job.  Backing up is highly recommended.  -- From Cymltaneous Solutions: http://cymlsol.cyml.cjb.net/.
